          <updateDate>2018-10-05T04:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Aircraft Avionics Systems Cybersecurity Act</strong></p> <p>This bill requires the Federal Aviation Administration to consider revising its regulations regarding airworthiness certification to: (1) address cybersecurity for avionics systems, and (2) require that aircraft avionics systems used for flight guidance or aircraft control be secured against unauthorized access by passenger inflight entertainment systems. </p>]]></text>
          <name>Introduced in House</name>
